our Business for a Professional Video Shoot"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-teal pl-4","children":"A little preparation before the camera crew arrives makes a huge difference in what you get out of the day. Here's how to set your shoot up for success."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/[0.06] mb-10"}]}],["$","article",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16","children":[[["$","p","0",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Hiring a professional video crew is a significant investment, and the return on that investment depends heavily on how prepared you are when they show up. The shoot day moves fast. Time spent figuring out logistics on location is time not spent getting great footage."]}],["$","p","1",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Here's how to prepare so you get the most out of the day."]}],["$","h2","2",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Start with a Clear Shot List"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["A shot list is exactly what it sounds like — a list of specific shots you need to capture. Work with your videographer in advance to develop this. Think about:"]}],["$","ul","4",{"className":"list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"What locations or settings need to be covered"}],["$","li","1",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"What products, services, or processes need to be shown"}],["$","li","2",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Who needs to be on camera and in what capacity"}],["$","li","3",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"What the final deliverable needs to accomplish"}]]}],["$","p","5",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["A good shot list doesn't have to be exhaustive, but it gives the crew a clear roadmap and prevents the end of the day from arriving before you've covered everything important."]}],["$","h2","6",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Prepare Your Space"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["If you're shooting at your business location:"]}],["$","p","8",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Clean and declutter"}]," — The camera sees everything. A messy background is distracting and hard to fix in post."]}],["$","p","9",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Check the lighting"}]," — If your space relies on fluorescent overhead lighting, talk to your videographer in advance. They may want to bring their own lighting or adjust what's there."]}],["$","p","10",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Control the noise"}]," — HVAC systems, street traffic, refrigeration units, and nearby construction all create audio problems. Walk through the space with sound in mind and identify anything that might need to be addressed."]}],["$","p","11",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Coordinate with your team"}]," — Make sure your staff knows a shoot is happening, who needs to be available, and what areas of the business need to remain accessible."]}],["$","h2","12",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Prepare Your On-Camera Talent"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["If anyone from your team will be speaking on camera, give them time to prepare. They don't need to memorize a script, but they should:"]}],["$","ul","14",{"className":"list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Know what they want to say and in what order"}],["$","li","1",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Practice saying it out loud before the day"}],["$","li","2",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Dress appropriately for your brand and the shoot environment"}],["$","li","3",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Get a good night's sleep beforehand"}]]}],["$","p","15",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Being on camera feels more unnatural than most people expect. Preparation reduces nerves and results in more confident, usable footage."]}],["$","h2","16",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Have Backup Plans"}],["$","p","17",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Things go wrong on shoot days. A key person gets sick. The weather changes. A location becomes unavailable. Think through your contingencies in advance so that a problem doesn't derail the entire day."]}],["$","h2","18",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Trust the Professionals"}],["$","p","19",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Once you've done the preparation, trust your crew. They've done this before. If they suggest a different angle, adjust the schedule, or recommend a change to the plan, listen. The goal is the best possible footage, and a good production team is your partner in getting there."]}],["$","p","20",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["The businesses that get the most out of their video shoots are the ones that come prepared and stay flexible. Show up organized, stay communicative, and let the professionals do what they do best."]}]],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal/10 to-transparent border border-teal/20 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest mb-3","children":"Find a Professional on the Gulf Coast"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted text-sm mb-6","children":"Browse verified media professionals available for your next project — from Tallahassee to New Orleans."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap","children":[["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/browse","className":"btn-teal font-display tracking-widest px-6 py-2","children":"Browse Pros"}],["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/post-job","className":"btn-outline font-display tracking-widest px-6 py-2","children":"Post a Job"}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-navy2 border-t border-white/[0.06] py-12 px-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-6xl mx-auto","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest mb-8 text-center","children":"More Guides"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5","children":[["$","$L2","drone-videography-what-you-need-to-know",{"href":"/blog/drone-videography-what-you-need-to-know","className":"card p-5 hover:border-teal/40 transition-all duration-200 group","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-condensed text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase bg-teal/10 text-teal border border-teal/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded mb-3 inline-block","children":"Hiring Tips"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-condensed text-sm tracking-wide text-white group-hover:text-teal transition-colors leading-snug","children":"Drone Videography: What You Need to Know Before You Hire"}]]}],["$","$L2","what-to-expect-from-professional-audio-engin